request.description:
Working

Usage:

- Get the first 10 books: `/books`
- Get the next 10 books: `/books/?limit=10&offset=10`
- Get 5 books starting from the 20th book: `/books/?limit=5&offset=19`

Working

Usage:

- Get the first 10 books with a 4 star rating: `/books/rating/4`
- Get the next 10 books with a 4 star rating: `/books/rating/4?limit=10&offset=10`
    
- Get 5 books starting from the 20th book with a 4 star rating: `/books/rating/4?limit=5&offset=19`

Working

Usage:

- Get the first 10 books with at least 4 star rating: `/books/minrating/4`
    
- Get the next 10 books with at least 4 star rating: `/books/minrating/4?limit=10&offset=10`
    
- Get 5 books starting from the 20th book with at least 4 star rating: `/books/minrating/4?limit=5&offset=19`
